{
  "stem": "17299.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew that from Germany how that was being done, especially with the cattle feed, because the beets which you feed the cattle and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they asked me how you do it, and I explained that to him, said, yeah, you know how.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how I got in that work kommando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would say probably until middle of December.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I-- was put in charge of the PX.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The PX was-- let's say 25 Jews were taken out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were deloused, got clean clothes, underwear, double set of underwear, another clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And two clean blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And march in a special building, separate building by the PX, where 20 men slept in one room, and five women in the other room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the middle was a kitchen. 19, 18 Jews worked in the food magazine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means 15, actually, because three worked in the PX.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And four women worked in the food magazine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one woman and another fellow worked in the housing for the SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The woman had to do the cooking for the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a Latvian fellow who was the shift cook in main hotel in Hamburg, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was our cook in Dondagen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we had better meals, prepared meals, than the SS had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was very strong and was very good at math, or knew how to handle certain things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which a lot of them did not, because they had grown up in the country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they picked out the-- the most, uh-- knowledgeable, and the strongest one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Germans had rations, what the soldiers could get an alcohol, cigarettes, razor blade, shaving cream, and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
